text:
Celebrations, Parades, and Municipal Events: Mayor John F. Hylan, Grover Whalen and others leading an unknown (to the writer) parade. This set consists of 4 views; Nos. 1 and 2 showing the line of march moving northward on Fifth Ave., after the start at Washington Square. Nos. 3 and 4 show eminent personages assembled on Washington Square North at Fifth Ave., prior to the start.

Prior to 1925.

Misc.
